Package fi.abo.kogni.soile2.projecthandling.projectElements

Class ElementDataHandler<T extends Element>

java.lang.Object
fi.abo.kogni.soile2.projecthandling.projectElements.ElementDataHandler<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The class of the Element handled by this handler
public class ElementDataHandler<T extends Element> extends Object
Handler for element data interaction between The Database and the Git Repository (i.e. linking the two sides.

Thomas Pfau

    • handlePostFile

      public io.vertx.core.Future<String> handlePostFile(String taskID, String taskVersion, String filename, SOILEUpload upload)
      Write a file from an upload to git. NOTE: This will remove the actual file of the upload and move it to the datalake
      Parameters:
      taskID - the ID of the task
      taskVersion - the version of the task BEFORE adding the file (i.e. base version)
      filename - The name of the file that is being added
      upload - the FileUpload that has the uploaded file.
      Returns:
      A Future of the Version String of the Task Version after the file was added
